actions.message:
Setting me up is a super-easy and convinient process.

1. Invite me to your server [here](https://discordapp.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=460908483030679563&scope=bot&permissions=2146958591).

2. Set up my custom logs by creating a channel for logs then entering ;logs {text channel}.
(You will need to set permissions for the log channel so random members can't send messages.)

3. Set up my welcome channel with ;welcome {text channel} {welcome message}.
(This will let you choose where you want me to put welcome messages.)

4. Set up my leave channel with ;leave {text channel} {leave message}.
(This will let you choose where you want me to put leave messages.)
